8_27	0.08507199	Luce professor in the human dimensions of global change at Carleton College in Northfield, Minn.
8_28	0.092643744	``In a way it's an elaborate fiction that allows people to say, `Isn't it great, these animals are being saved'.
8_29	0.075856539	'' In fact, the vast majority of programs have failed to meet expectations.
