21_29	0.24532805	There is no evidence that a naturally occurring wolf population existed in Yellowstone or central Idaho prior to the introduction of the gray wolves.
21_30	0.169103	Therefore, concluded the appellate court, on that question, the Department of the Interior did not violate the Endangered Species Act.
